    <refname>Closed loop poles and zeros</refname>

    <refpurpose> Closed loop poles and zeros</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>


  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para> Closed loop poles and zeros can
be seen in two ways. (1) Select 'Response-->Details'.
This will bring up a menu that shows the numerical
values of pole(s) and zeros(s) at the current gain as
seen in the slider. (2) Select 'Response-->Closed loop'.
Select 'Closed loop poles' in the menu that comes up.</para>

  </refsection>


